  <brief_title>Proof-of-concept for the Aldosterone Synthase Inhibitor LCI699 in Patients With Primary Hyperaldosteronism</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot, Single-blind, Forced-titration Study to Assess the Hemodynamic and Hormonal Effects, Safety and Tolerability of the Aldosterone Synthase Inhibitor LCI699 in Patients With Primary Hyperaldosteronism</official_title>
  <sponsors>
